You failed the mission

32
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:09,770
to get the White-Eyed Blue Dragon.

33
00:03:10,340 --> 00:03:13,270
Don't fail again this time.

34
00:03:13,270 --> 00:03:14,180
I understand.

35
00:03:19,380 --> 00:03:22,060
Gone is my nice weekend.

36
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:35,300
(Please choose the costume for High Saint's Day
Lolita  /  Hanfu)

37
00:03:35,300 --> 00:03:37,150
(Hanfu)

38
00:03:39,430 --> 00:03:43,120
(High Saint's Day)

39
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:44,210
I must say

40
00:03:44,330 --> 00:03:46,690
that rituals in Huaxiu are very exciting.

41
00:03:47,250 --> 00:03:47,810
Alright.

42
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:50,870
I should be able to enter the park
if I go with these people.

43
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,550
Hold on, miss.

44
00:03:53,180 --> 00:03:54,000
What is it?

45
00:03:54,300 --> 00:03:55,380
Where is your partner?

46
00:03:55,900 --> 00:03:56,880
What partner?

47
00:03:57,810 --> 00:03:59,500
(Notice) (Forbidden to Enter: Tangs    Singles)
According to the Chairman's regulations,

48
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:02,340
(Notice) (Forbidden to Enter: Tangs    Singles)
you must have a partner in order to enter the park.

49
00:04:02,340 --> 00:04:03,000
(Notice) (Forbidden to Enter: Tangs    Singles)

50
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:05,050
(Notice) (Forbidden to Enter: Tangs    Singles)
It's a discrimination against single people.

51
00:04:05,660 --> 00:04:06,270
Don't worry.

52
00:04:06,530 --> 00:04:08,000
(Forbidden to Enter: Jiugong   Tangs  Singles)
You are not the only one who doesn't have a partner.

53
00:04:08,460 --> 00:04:09,430
They are all singles.

54
00:04:09,430 --> 00:04:10,720
You are an outstanding lady.

55
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,280
I'm sure you'll find one that suits you.

56
00:04:12,460 --> 00:04:13,310
Ah.

57
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:16,520
Is this the legendary match-making corner?

58
00:04:18,060 --> 00:04:20,390
(According to High Saint's Day traditions,
visitors must enter the park in pairs.)

59
00:04:20,390 --> 00:04:23,680
(Who would you choose to enter the park with?
Li Xiaoyu / Guo Hao / Chen Chao)

60
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:25,440
(Singles)

61
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:27,850
She is Lin Xiaoyu from Class Elite.

62
00:04:28,190 --> 00:04:30,570
She always looks harmless to anyone.

63
00:04:30,810 --> 00:04:31,870
I'll pick her.

64
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:34,890
Oh la la. You are Xiaoyu, aren't you?

65
00:04:35,190 --> 00:04:37,060
You are dressed so beautifully tonight

66
00:04:37,140 --> 00:04:38,980
that I didn't recognize you at first sight.

67
00:04:38,980 --> 00:04:40,640
Ah. Haha...

68
00:04:40,820 --> 00:04:42,000
Thank you.

69
00:04:42,610 --> 00:04:44,610
Xiaoyu, let's go in together.

70
00:04:44,810 --> 00:04:45,560
Ah?

71
00:04:45,930 --> 00:04:48,570
I'm waiting for Uncle Sun to take me into the park.

72
00:04:48,570 --> 00:04:51,690
What a coincidence.
I'm waiting for Uncle Sun too.

73
00:04:51,690 --> 00:04:52,310
Ah?

74
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,680
No kidding?

75
00:04:53,860 --> 00:04:54,640
Of course not.

76
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:58,250
My purpose of coming to Huaxiu
is to exchange our cultures

77
00:04:58,370 --> 00:05:00,880
and experience the life of Huaxiu people.

78
00:05:01,310 --> 00:05:03,880
Experience the life of Huaxiu people?

79
00:05:04,010 --> 00:05:04,760
Exactly.

80
00:05:05,190 --> 00:05:08,240
The annual High Saint's Day is a rare chance.

81
00:05:08,370 --> 00:05:10,510
I hope you can help me fulfill my wish.

82
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,200
Alright.

83
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,050
But you are from a wealthy family.

84
00:05:15,050 --> 00:05:16,180
Are you sure you
won't have any problems with it?

85
00:05:16,350 --> 00:05:18,720
Definitely. What problems can I have?

86
00:05:19,550 --> 00:05:21,140
The celebration on High Saint's Day
is a big event.

87
00:05:21,310 --> 00:05:22,540
It can be very tiring.

88
00:05:23,260 --> 00:05:26,490
Xiaoyu, don't say that again.

89
00:05:26,810 --> 00:05:29,430
Don't sort me out because of my family.

90
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:31,680
Am I not eligible?

91
00:05:32,370 --> 00:05:33,760
Okay.

92
00:05:34,180 --> 00:05:36,560
Uncle Sun, I'm here.

93
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,270
Ah.

94
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:40,810
Sorry. I was a little busy with something.

95
00:05:41,330 --> 00:05:42,480
This is...

96
00:05:43,070 --> 00:05:44,100
She is...

97
00:05:44,100 --> 00:05:45,180
Don't you remember me, Uncle Sun?

98
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:47,390
I'm Xiaoyu's schoolmate.

99
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:48,640
Ah?

100
00:05:49,250 --> 00:05:50,480
Oh oh.

101
00:05:50,510 --> 00:05:52,540
Yes, you are Xiaoyu's schoolmate.

102
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:55,420
Perfect. We are very busy tonight
and need more hands.

103
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:56,750
Why don't you come along?

104
00:05:57,890 --> 00:05:58,450
Okay.

105
00:05:59,410 --> 00:06:00,110
En?

106
00:06:00,500 --> 00:06:01,870
Need more hands?

107
00:06:04,330 --> 00:06:06,300
Table No. 8 ordered 20 pan-fried rices.

108
00:06:07,330 --> 00:06:09,170
You aides, do it fast.

109
00:06:10,550 --> 00:06:12,500
The curry chickens are ready.
I need more dishes.

110
00:06:12,500 --> 00:06:13,450
Coming.

111
00:06:13,750 --> 00:06:15,500
Get some radishes from the stockroom. Quick.

112
00:06:16,670 --> 00:06:17,550
Excuse me. Let me through.

113
00:06:18,300 --> 00:06:19,450
Here come the dishes.

114
00:06:20,580 --> 00:06:21,670
Careful. Watch it.

115
00:06:22,550 --> 00:06:23,870
Who am I?

116
00:06:24,500 --> 00:06:25,920
Where am I?

117
00:06:26,170 --> 00:06:26,950
Come on.

118
00:06:27,700 --> 00:06:29,050
Let's change into these.

119
00:06:30,250 --> 00:06:32,200
Table No. 8 ordered 20 pan-fried rices.

120
00:06:33,250 --> 00:06:34,930
You aides, do it fast.

121
00:06:34,930 --> 00:06:36,290
Xiaoyu, it's about time.

122
00:06:36,430 --> 00:06:37,970
I'll leave these 200 dishes to you.

123
00:06:38,290 --> 00:06:38,910
Fine.

124
00:06:39,130 --> 00:06:40,830
New comer, go to clean the cups.

125
00:06:41,350 --> 00:06:43,560
Workers Are Human Beings

126
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:46,250
I didn't know Lin Xiaoyu was coming here to work.
Workers Are Human Beings

127
00:06:46,250 --> 00:06:46,800
Workers Are Human Beings

128
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,470
Otherwise, I wouldn't have picked her.
Workers Are Human Beings

129
00:06:48,470 --> 00:06:49,350
Workers Are Human Beings

130
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:53,520
My god. It's going to take forever

131
00:06:53,750 --> 00:06:55,330
to clean all these cups.

132
00:06:55,610 --> 00:06:57,360
Xiaoyu, have you washed all the dishes?

133
00:06:57,740 --> 00:06:58,540
I have.

134
00:06:58,750 --> 00:06:59,440
What?

135
00:06:59,970 --> 00:07:01,290
So fast?

136
00:07:01,430 --> 00:07:02,680
She really works hard.

137
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:05,450
Go over there and
wash the 200-jin (220 pounds) cabbages.

138
00:07:05,890 --> 00:07:06,570
Right on it.

139
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:10,720
Is this how they work in Huaxiu?

140
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:12,250
New comer, do your job.

141
00:07:12,250 --> 00:07:12,860
Ah?

142
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:15,330
Ah, okay, okay.

143
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:17,170
What job?

144
00:07:17,860 --> 00:07:19,370
This is disgusting.

145
00:07:19,930 --> 00:07:22,320
I'm the young lady of the Jiugong family

146
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:26,160
and they ask me to do such nasty work
for the Sun family.

147
00:07:26,740 --> 00:07:27,880
Sun Rong,

148
00:07:28,230 --> 00:07:31,360
I'll make you pay for it, blood for blood.

149
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:32,810
You two,

150
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,490
go to prepare the lamb skewers
after you're finished with the dishes.

151
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:35,360
Yes.

152
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:39,360
Oh dear.

153
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:41,140
So much lamb.

154
00:07:41,140 --> 00:07:43,000
I have to work until the end of time.

155
00:07:43,270 --> 00:07:44,240
Jiugong

156
00:07:44,750 --> 00:07:46,300
I didn't expect
that a girl from a wealthy family

157
00:07:46,420 --> 00:07:47,770
would work here.

158
00:07:49,290 --> 00:07:50,600
I didn't expect

159
00:07:51,190 --> 00:07:54,120
that the life of a worker could be so hard.

160
00:07:55,410 --> 00:07:56,320
It's fine.

161
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:57,950
Much better than moving granite
on a construction site

162
00:07:57,950 --> 00:07:59,620
or digging for spiritual stones in a mine.

163
00:08:00,190 --> 00:08:00,850
Right.

164
00:08:01,310 --> 00:08:03,890
I'll try to persuade her to work
for the Jiugong family.

165
00:08:05,310 --> 00:08:05,980
Wait.

166
00:08:06,770 --> 00:08:08,500
Did I forget something?

167
00:08:09,250 --> 00:08:10,630
I'm here to steal the cudgel,

168
00:08:10,630 --> 00:08:12,320
not to work.

169
00:08:13,610 --> 00:08:16,050
Xiaoyu, do you often come to work
in the Sun family?

170
00:08:16,730 --> 00:08:17,270
Yes,

171
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:19,110
thanks to Sister Sun Rong.

172
00:08:19,250 --> 00:08:21,880
I have always wanted to
visit the Sun's main hall.

173
00:08:21,940 --> 00:08:23,730
Can you take me in there?

174
00:08:23,860 --> 00:08:24,810
Err...

175
00:08:24,930 --> 00:08:28,060
Generally, non-family members
are not permitted to go into the main hall.

176
00:08:28,140 --> 00:08:29,250
I need two to serve.

177
00:08:30,250 --> 00:08:30,930
Coming.

178
00:08:32,140 --> 00:08:33,580
Serve this dish to the Sun's main hall,

179
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,920
and the drinks to the square
in front of the hall.

180
00:08:36,190 --> 00:08:40,150
(You managed to enter the park and
become a kitchen aide.  You would choose...
serve the dish    serve the drink)

181
00:08:40,150 --> 00:08:41,750
(serve the drink)

182
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:47,210
20 meters to go.

183
00:08:47,610 --> 00:08:48,850
I can do it.

184
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,300
Be careful.

185
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:54,080
If the stew is spilled,
it will be deducted from your wage.

186
00:08:54,700 --> 00:08:55,870
I understand.

187
00:08:58,280 --> 00:09:00,120
Idiots.

188
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:03,280
Why did they stack them
before they are served.

189
00:09:03,400 --> 00:09:05,000
Put the champagne stack in place quickly.

190
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,160
There is more work to do in the kitchen.

191
00:09:06,900 --> 00:09:07,900
Copy that.

192
00:09:11,830 --> 00:09:13,080
Finally done.

193
00:09:13,570 --> 00:09:16,630
Next, find a way to get into the main hall.

194
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,620
Mmm.

195
00:09:19,170 --> 00:09:20,760
The soft taste

196
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:23,290
is long lasting and refreshing.

197
00:09:23,910 --> 00:09:25,580
If I am right,

198
00:09:25,620 --> 00:09:29,030
you cooked the stew personally, didn't you?

199
00:09:29,290 --> 00:09:29,860
Ah?

200
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:31,420
No.

201
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:33,750
You are being too modest, miss.

202
00:09:33,970 --> 00:09:37,100
In this world, only a beauty girl like you

203
00:09:37,350 --> 00:09:40,080
could have cooked such luscious pear stew.

204
00:09:40,130 --> 00:09:40,870
Excuse me.

205
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:43,100
Please don't affect my work.

206
00:09:43,450 --> 00:09:44,620
Work?

207
00:09:46,160 --> 00:09:47,580
Now that you are at work,

208
00:09:48,040 --> 00:09:51,050
why do you carry
a high-grade spiritual treasure with you?

209
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:54,160
I...I don't know what you are talking about.

210
00:09:55,380 --> 00:09:55,980
Ay.

211
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:59,100
There is a stick-shaped treasure
hidden in your sleeve.

212
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:01,460
Do I have the honor to take a look?

213
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:05,790
(You are at the market street and
is suspected by Lord Thunder.  You would choose...
confront him    run away)

214
00:10:05,790 --> 00:10:07,450
(run away)

215
00:10:11,670 --> 00:10:12,800
That's it.

216
00:10:21,790 --> 00:10:23,260
My pear stew.

217
00:10:24,970 --> 00:10:26,420
Luckily, I dodged quick enough.

218
00:10:28,750 --> 00:10:29,790
Where is the girl?

219
00:10:32,300 --> 00:10:33,710
Xiaoyu, are you alright?

220
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,990
I'll take you inside to change your dress.

221
00:10:41,410 --> 00:10:42,100
Stop.

222
00:10:42,540 --> 00:10:43,700
This is a no-entry area.

223
00:10:44,440 --> 00:10:45,710
Don't you have any sympathy at all?

224
00:10:45,860 --> 00:10:47,080
Can't you see?

225
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:48,610
Her dress is all wet.

226
00:10:48,850 --> 00:10:51,920
Ah? Oh, the dressing room
is on the corner on the first floor.

227
00:10:58,520 --> 00:11:00,090
Let me go in there alone.

228
00:11:00,450 --> 00:11:01,470
You can wait for me at the door.

229
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:02,300
Okay.

230
00:11:05,830 --> 00:11:08,200
I didn't expect to get in so easily.

231
00:11:08,690 --> 00:11:12,160
The Sun's security is slack.

232
00:11:12,830 --> 00:11:15,350
However, there are so many rooms here.

233
00:11:15,690 --> 00:11:18,620
Which room is the Sun's Sacred Cudgel in?

234
00:11:19,050 --> 00:11:22,610
My father's private money is hidden
in a secret chamber behind the bookcase.

235
00:11:23,370 --> 00:11:27,420
The Sun's treasure
must be hidden in a similar place.

236
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:29,070
Sister Jiugong,

237
00:11:29,290 --> 00:11:30,760
I can't fasten my dress.

238
00:11:30,980 --> 00:11:32,450
Can you come in and help me out?

239
00:11:33,050 --> 00:11:35,090
(You knocked over the champagne stack
and got Li Xiaoyu wet.)

240
00:11:35,090 --> 00:11:37,290
(You took Li Xiaoyu to the dressing room
in the Main Hall.  You would choose...
leave        help Li Xiaoyu)

241
00:11:37,290 --> 00:11:38,700
(help Li Xiaoyu)

242
00:11:40,350 --> 00:11:41,640
Xiaoyu, I'm coming.

243
00:11:45,130 --> 00:11:46,120
Sister Jiugong,

244
00:11:46,570 --> 00:11:47,760
help me fasten it.

245
00:11:51,190 --> 00:11:52,470
Let's go back to the kitchen now.

246
00:11:52,660 --> 00:11:54,120
They'll cut our pay
if we go back too late.

247
00:11:54,920 --> 00:11:57,590
No, I have a mission to accomplish.

248
00:11:58,170 --> 00:11:59,770
It is not my goal to work in this place.

249
00:12:01,300 --> 00:12:02,550
Well, Xiaoyu,

250
00:12:02,640 --> 00:12:06,330
they say they will show a big stick
toward the end of the High Saint's Day ritual.

251
00:12:06,570 --> 00:12:07,200
That's right.

252
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:10,350
It's the Sun's family heirloom,
the Sun's Sacred Cudgel.

253
00:12:10,490 --> 00:12:12,360
Yes, that's what I mean.

254
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:14,740
Do you know where the cudgel is kept?

255
00:12:15,070 --> 00:12:17,380
In the arsenal
in the basement of this building.

256
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:20,890
En...Sister Jiugong.

257
00:12:24,420 --> 00:12:25,870
So easy.

258
00:12:26,090 --> 00:12:29,100
Even a worker of the Sun family
knows where the cudgel is.

259
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:31,370
Does the Sun family
have no protective measures at all?

260
00:12:37,990 --> 00:12:38,700
You...

261
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:40,780
How can you lift it?

262
00:12:41,400 --> 00:12:43,030
It's impossible.

263
00:12:44,780 --> 00:12:45,400
It's...

264
00:12:45,830 --> 00:12:48,700
It's the Sun's Sacred Cudgel
handed down in the family.

265
